snippet.title: Call of Mini: Zombies 2.0 Multiplayer Trailer
snippet.description:
In response to player demand we've added CO-OP MULTIPLAYER, coming very soon! Team up with your buddies and survive wave after wave of vile zombies! How long can you last?

Download Call of Mini: Zombies now!
http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/call-of-mini-zombies/id431213733?mt=8

Follow Triniti on twitter for info on our latest releases, updates, and FREE games: http://www.twitter.com/TrinitiGames
